        "Hello Bob, how are you?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个循环场景。那Bob的回复分支怎么设计？是简单的二选一还是有更多情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loop",
        "alt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用alt分支处理两种情况：如果Bob生病了，回复\"Not so good\"带个难过的表情；如果身体好，就说\"Feeling fresh like a daisy\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alt",
        "is sick",
        "is well",
        "Not so good :(",
        "Feeling fresh like a daisy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把循环结构和alt分支画出来，Alice发起问候，Bob根据状态选择回复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "loop Daily query",
        "Alice-Bob",
        "Bob-Alice",
        "alt",
        "else"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚注意到分支条件写反了，\"is sick\"应该对应\"Not so good\"，\"is well\"对应积极的回复。我调整一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alt is sick",
        "else is well"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，还可以加个可选环节：有时候Bob会额外说一句\"Thanks for asking\"，但不是每次都出现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "opt",
        "Extra response",
        "Thanks for asking"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，这个opt放在alt分支结束之后、循环结束之前，对吗？这样每次问候后都有可能触发感谢语。",
      "elements_involved": [
